sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Python app
    participant DogPy as Dog owned
    participant CDLL as _native CDLL
    participant Bridge as bridge.cpp
    participant Pool as HandlePool
    participant AO_Owned as AnimalObject owned
    participant AO_View as AnimalObject view
    participant CatPy as Cat borrowed

    App->>DogPy: Dog.create(...)
    DogPy->>CDLL: dog_create(...)
    CDLL->>Bridge: extern C call
    Bridge->>Bridge: make Dog with unique_ptr Cat friend
    Bridge->>Pool: store AnimalObject unique_ptr Dog
    Pool->>AO_Owned: owns unique_ptr Animal Dog
    Note over AO_Owned: Dog holds unique_ptr Cat friend
    Pool-->>Bridge: handle 1
    Bridge-->>DogPy: int64_t handle owned=True
    DogPy-->>App: Dog handle=1

    App->>DogPy: friend or friend_cat
    DogPy->>CDLL: animal_friend_ptr 1
    CDLL->>Bridge: extern C call
    Bridge->>AO_Owned: dog friend_cat returns Cat raw ptr
    Note over AO_Owned: Cat still owned by Dog unique_ptr
    Bridge->>Pool: ensure_view_handle Cat ptr
    Pool->>AO_View: store AnimalObject Cat ptr only
    Note over AO_View: view holds Cat ptr no ownership
    Pool-->>Bridge: handle 2
    Bridge-->>DogPy: int64_t handle 2
    DogPy-->>App: Cat handle=2 owned=False

    App->>CatPy: close borrowed wrapper
    Note over CatPy: owned=False no handle_release
    CatPy-->>App: Python ref dropped view pool entry kept

    App->>DogPy: close owned wrapper
    DogPy->>CDLL: handle_release 1
    CDLL->>Bridge: extern C call
    Bridge->>Pool: remove_view_handles_for handle 2
    Pool->>AO_View: erase view entry only
    Note over AO_View: does not delete Cat object
    Bridge->>Pool: release handle 1
    Pool->>AO_Owned: erase owned entry
    AO_Owned->>AO_Owned: ~unique_ptr Animal destroys Dog
    Note over AO_Owned: Dog destructor deletes Cat unique_ptr
    Pool-->>Bridge: done
    Bridge-->>App: handle 1 and 2 invalid
